{"tid":2478033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛表示中國科興跟國藥疫苗　須拿出更多數據証明安全有效","createTime":"2021-04-06T17:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T18:13:30.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19ab5ee3f115484ac395c2ecd6a9c5d35efe781b","tid":2478033,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.hkgolden.com/【世衛表示中國科興跟國藥疫苗須拿出更多數據証/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.hkgolden.com%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E8%B7%9F%E5%9C%8B%E8%97%A5%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E9%A0%88%E6%8B%BF%E5%87%BA%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%A8%BC%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=2658b6e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.hkgolden.com/【世衛表示中國科興跟國藥疫苗須拿出更多數據証/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.hkgolden.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/fcvafsfsa-696x696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.hkgolden.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Ffcvafsfsa-696x696.jpg&h=436dc015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，世界衛生組織（31日）表示，根據對中國科興、國藥武漢肺炎疫苗數據的中期分析顯示，兩款疫苗看起來都安全且有效，但如果要取得世衛的接種推薦，中國必須拿出更多數據。<br />\n<br />\n世衛的免疫專家戰略諮詢小組指出，他們檢視了中方提供的所有數據，兩種疫苗皆「證明了自身地安全性，也能有效預防武肺症狀」，但小組也提出了警告「兩隻疫苗都缺乏高齡族群的接種數據，而共病症狀方面的資訊也並不足夠。」小組專家暗示疫苗有機會導致其他情況發生。截至目前只有輝瑞/BNT、牛津/AZ、強生3種疫苗獲得世衛的認可。"},{"pid":"3c9239bbc99b8b22b5cf124d64d214c16d78ef3a","tid":2478033,"uid":123988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"今個月比唔夠錢咩？"},{"pid":"f9afbecfc2739ed034e9dd01991a1ecb35490c0a","tid":2478033,"uid":278038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:01:25.000Z","msg":"過唔到數呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1e406090172009c37ec8e71fc4b14d2c54894d","tid":2478033,"uid":47810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"WHO：之前畀嘅錢用曬，加錢呀！